WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:02.110
Good morning, family. I have another video

00:00:02.120 --> 00:00:05.349
for you. This one I've not

00:00:05.359 --> 00:00:09.390
wanted to do, but I need to, so here

00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:13.390
you go. This has been

00:00:13.400 --> 00:00:14.910
something that everybody wants

00:00:14.920 --> 00:00:17.830
to know about—about Brandon, about me, about my

00:00:17.840 --> 00:00:19.950
life, about what I've been through and

00:00:19.960 --> 00:00:21.349
things like that—and I'm just going to

00:00:21.359 --> 00:00:26.830
give you a little bit of it.

00:00:26.840 --> 00:00:29.710
I'm trying to think of how to even

00:00:29.720 --> 00:00:32.150
start it. There's

00:00:32.160 --> 00:00:36.030
so much pain, there's so much stuff, and

00:00:36.040 --> 00:00:39.950
I struggle a lot talking about it.

00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:41.950
So,

00:00:41.960 --> 00:00:46.869
here you

00:00:46.879 --> 00:00:52.470
go. My little girl, back whenever she was

00:00:52.480 --> 00:00:57.069
18 months old, there was a

00:00:57.079 --> 00:01:00.270
bad flu epidemic going around, and so a

00:01:00.280 --> 00:01:02.069
lot of people from the church were

00:01:02.079 --> 00:01:05.789
encouraging us to get the flu

00:01:05.799 --> 00:01:09.149
shot.

00:01:09.159 --> 00:01:10.990
We talked to our doctor at the hospital

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:12.710
and

00:01:12.720 --> 00:01:15.030
they were pushing vaccinations really

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:17.789
hard. They said, "Oh yeah, you

00:01:17.789 --> 00:01:17.799
could

00:01:17.799 --> 00:01:19.510
definitely be hospitalized for

00:01:19.510 --> 00:01:19.520
this."She

00:01:19.520 --> 00:01:21.830
was 18

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:25.149
months old and she was already

00:01:25.159 --> 00:01:28.230
developing; her Apgar scores were okay,

00:01:28.240 --> 00:01:30.149
everything was okay. She was already

00:01:30.159 --> 00:01:32.550
starting to say little

00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:34.469
words and do little things here and

00:01:34.479 --> 00:01:36.429
there. Her eye contact—everything was

00:01:36.439 --> 00:01:39.429
normal. We went in and got the

00:01:39.439 --> 00:01:42.149
vaccination, and we went home that

00:01:42.159 --> 00:01:45.990
night and my baby was screaming and

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:48.230
things were really different. She started

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:51.389
running a really high fever, and

00:01:51.399 --> 00:01:54.950
within about a

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:58.910
week, her whole mind changed. Everything

00:01:58.920 --> 00:02:01.709
changed.

00:02:01.719 --> 00:02:05.670
She lost all verbal

00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:09.029
communication, her bowels stopped moving,

00:02:09.039 --> 00:02:11.630
her stomach swelled up like a beach

00:02:11.640 --> 00:02:15.470
ball, she stopped eating, and she went into

00:02:15.480 --> 00:02:17.390
this

00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:22.550
bubble. She cried all the time

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:25.790
continuously, from the time she got up to

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:28.030
the time she went to bed. She

00:02:28.040 --> 00:02:31.030
cried, she hummed, she made weird noises,

00:02:31.040 --> 00:02:33.270
and she

00:02:33.280 --> 00:02:37.190
rocked. I can honestly tell you, we

00:02:37.200 --> 00:02:40.630
didn't know what was going on.

00:02:40.640 --> 00:02:42.350
We called the doctor

00:02:42.360 --> 00:02:45.910
and said there's a problem. She

00:02:45.920 --> 00:02:48.990
said, "Okay, come in and

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:50.589
I'll examine her and see what's

00:02:50.599 --> 00:02:52.630
going on."She goes, "Well, you know, some

00:02:52.640 --> 00:02:55.550
kids just have reactions sometimes to

00:02:55.560 --> 00:02:57.910
shots, so don't worry about it; she'll

00:02:57.920 --> 00:03:02.350
come out of

00:03:02.350 --> 00:03:02.360
it."No,

00:03:02.360 --> 00:03:05.470
she didn't come out of

00:03:05.480 --> 00:03:09.710
it. Weeks went by and she got

00:03:09.720 --> 00:03:12.190
worse. Things were so bad that she would

00:03:12.200 --> 00:03:15.110
only sleep two hours a night.

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:19.030
I got two hours of sleep at night for

00:03:19.040 --> 00:03:21.750
months. She kept me up all night long and

00:03:21.760 --> 00:03:23.190
I would sit in the rocking chair and

00:03:23.200 --> 00:03:25.949
just cry myself to sleep holding

00:03:25.959 --> 00:03:28.630
her. I'd find her in there just

00:03:28.640 --> 00:03:31.350
screaming, and it was

00:03:31.360 --> 00:03:33.670
awful. I had to go to work the next day

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:35.429
and I'd fall asleep at work because I

00:03:35.439 --> 00:03:38.350
couldn't function; I was so tired. My

00:03:38.360 --> 00:03:42.149
wife was going through literal hell

00:03:42.159 --> 00:03:43.750
whenever I was at

00:03:43.760 --> 00:03:46.990
work with her throwing fits and

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:49.110
tantrums. It went

00:03:49.120 --> 00:03:52.509
on and on, and finally, we went

00:03:52.519 --> 00:03:54.509
to the doctor and said there's

00:03:54.519 --> 00:03:56.710
something bad that's happened and we

00:03:56.720 --> 00:03:58.670
need to know what's going on with our

00:03:58.680 --> 00:04:03.110
daughter. She just kind of

00:04:03.110 --> 00:04:03.120
pooh-poohed

00:04:03.120 --> 00:04:04.949
us off like, "Well, she'll

00:04:04.959 --> 00:04:07.270
come out of it."We got a certified letter

00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:10.350
in the mail telling us not to come back

00:04:10.360 --> 00:04:13.789
to the doctor. She fired us as patients.

00:04:13.799 --> 00:04:15.949
She blamed it on us being late for

00:04:15.959 --> 00:04:18.270
our appointments too many times and told

00:04:18.280 --> 00:04:21.030
us not to come back. We tried to get a

00:04:21.040 --> 00:04:22.629
hold of the office and she wouldn't

00:04:22.639 --> 00:04:25.670
respond or talk to us anymore. It was

00:04:25.680 --> 00:04:29.070
a total abandonment. We

00:04:29.080 --> 00:04:31.029
didn't know what to do; we were in our

00:04:31.039 --> 00:04:34.310
20s when this happened. We told family

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:36.710
and friends what had happened, and

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:38.790
everybody was like, "Wow, this is crazy, you

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:42.950
need to hire an attorney."I

00:04:42.950 --> 00:04:42.960
said,

00:04:42.960 --> 00:04:45.270
"We're

00:04:45.280 --> 00:04:47.110
not doing all that; I need to have more

00:04:48.909 --> 00:04:48.919
wisdom."The

00:04:52.759 --> 00:04:56.550
process kept happening. Years go by, and

00:04:56.560 --> 00:05:00.070
I kept standing by faith and

00:05:00.070 --> 00:05:00.080
believing

00:05:00.080 --> 00:05:02.670
that everything was going to be okay.

00:05:02.680 --> 00:05:05.270
I wouldn't allow anybody to speak

00:05:05.280 --> 00:05:07.909
any negative around us; we

00:05:07.919 --> 00:05:11.469
just closed ourselves off. She started

00:05:11.479 --> 00:05:13.189
pulling all the stuff out of the

00:05:13.199 --> 00:05:15.909
drawers in our kitchen. She would

00:05:15.919 --> 00:05:18.390
take everything from the

00:05:18.390 --> 00:05:18.400
cupboard

00:05:18.400 --> 00:05:20.110
and put it in the bathroom; you

00:05:20.120 --> 00:05:21.830
never knew where something was going to

00:05:21.840 --> 00:05:24.350
be. She started playing with her feces on

00:05:24.360 --> 00:05:26.710
a day-to-day basis. She would walk up and

00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:29.270
down the halls and rub her feces

00:05:29.280 --> 00:05:31.430
down the hall, or wipe feces all over

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:33.790
our couch. She would play with

00:05:33.800 --> 00:05:35.270
it

00:05:35.280 --> 00:05:39.110
continually. On top of not sleeping

00:05:39.110 --> 00:05:39.120
and

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:42.469
everything else, she would not eat and she

00:05:42.479 --> 00:05:44.469
would cry continually. We couldn't go

00:05:44.479 --> 00:05:46.590
inside any stores or go

00:05:46.600 --> 00:05:49.350
anywhere with her because of how bad her

00:05:49.360 --> 00:05:52.510
behavior was. So, we started seeking

00:05:52.520 --> 00:05:56.110
help.

00:05:56.120 --> 00:05:59.150
People started telling us, "We

00:05:59.160 --> 00:06:00.590
believe there's something

00:06:00.600 --> 00:06:02.350
seriously going on with your daughter,

00:06:02.360 --> 00:06:07.070
but we're going to have to do a lot of

00:06:07.070 --> 00:06:07.080
testing."All

00:06:07.080 --> 00:06:10.909
this to say, they labeled her

00:06:10.919 --> 00:06:12.749
as severely

00:06:12.759 --> 00:06:16.990
autistic. It

00:06:16.990 --> 00:06:17.000
was

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:21.029
the biggest sucker

00:06:21.039 --> 00:06:25.189
punch. I

00:06:25.199 --> 00:06:27.550
didn't know what to

00:06:27.560 --> 00:06:30.469
do, and all I could do

00:06:30.479 --> 00:06:32.189
because of my faith

00:06:33.800 --> 00:06:41.790
was just to keep

00:06:41.800 --> 00:06:44.070
standing. They told us she would never

00:06:44.080 --> 00:06:47.270
talk, she would never have a normal life,

00:06:47.270 --> 00:06:47.280
and

00:06:47.280 --> 00:06:49.350
she would probably always be in diapers

00:06:52.319 --> 00:06:55.189
forever.

00:06:55.199 --> 00:06:57.550
Family and friends didn't

00:06:57.560 --> 00:07:01.909
really know what to do with it;

00:07:01.919 --> 00:07:04.230
everybody started to say it was a devil,

00:07:04.240 --> 00:07:05.790
"You need to go get the devils cast out

00:07:05.800 --> 00:07:07.270
of your little

00:07:07.270 --> 00:07:07.280
girl."We

00:07:07.280 --> 00:07:10.189
went to a big ministry down

00:07:10.199 --> 00:07:10.909
in

00:07:10.919 --> 00:07:14.550
Dallas to get these devils out of her

00:07:14.560 --> 00:07:18.070
because of this disorder called

00:07:18.080 --> 00:07:20.189
autism. They said she needed

00:07:20.199 --> 00:07:22.390
deliverance, so we paid a

00:07:22.400 --> 00:07:24.950
ministry $500 to cast the devils out of

00:07:24.960 --> 00:07:27.029
her because we were so new

00:07:27.039 --> 00:07:27.990
at

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:33.790
this. We got ripped off, basically

00:07:33.800 --> 00:07:37.869
scammed. Everybody has a

00:07:37.879 --> 00:07:40.830
cure for it. We spent thousands and

00:07:40.840 --> 00:07:43.150
thousands of

00:07:43.150 --> 00:07:43.160
dollars—everything

00:07:43.160 --> 00:07:45.869
we could on credit

00:07:45.869 --> 00:07:45.879
cards—to

00:07:45.879 --> 00:07:48.110
try to get her help.

00:07:49.639 --> 00:07:51.270
You

00:07:51.280 --> 00:07:53.830
listen to these people

00:07:53.840 --> 00:07:56.029
on the internet, and

00:07:56.039 --> 00:07:57.749
you're Googling trying to find the

00:07:57.759 --> 00:08:00.070
answer to help your

00:08:00.080 --> 00:08:02.469
child who's absolutely in this

00:08:02.479 --> 00:08:05.149
weird bubble.

00:08:05.159 --> 00:08:07.070
They say you

00:08:07.080 --> 00:08:09.749
can do all these therapies, and

00:08:09.759 --> 00:08:12.189
I'm still standing on the word,

00:08:12.199 --> 00:08:14.070
but I would not allow anybody to say that

00:08:14.080 --> 00:08:15.950
she's autistic around me or I'd want to

00:08:15.960 --> 00:08:17.909
punch you in the face. That's how angry I

00:08:17.919 --> 00:08:19.790
was at the

00:08:19.800 --> 00:08:22.029
circumstance because I didn't understand.

00:08:40.800 --> 00:08:43.110
It felt like literal hell on

00:08:43.120 --> 00:08:46.590
earth. The

00:08:46.600 --> 00:08:48.590
pressure was

00:08:48.600 --> 00:08:51.829
horrendous and it

00:08:51.839 --> 00:08:52.870
wouldn't

00:08:52.880 --> 00:08:56.190
stop. We started

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:58.110
ABA therapy.

00:08:58.120 --> 00:08:59.430
It

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:01.310
was very expensive, over a hundred

00:09:01.320 --> 00:09:03.790
dollars an hour.

00:09:03.800 --> 00:09:04.910
We were just putting it

00:09:04.920 --> 00:09:06.470
on credit cards

00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:07.710
and

00:09:07.720 --> 00:09:10.310
shuffling

00:09:10.320 --> 00:09:13.350
things around all we could.

00:09:16.839 --> 00:09:20.550
Our church tried

00:09:20.560 --> 00:09:23.630
to help us out as much as they could.

00:09:28.480 --> 00:09:30.389
I don't want to

00:09:30.399 --> 00:09:33.069
keep rambling over this;

00:09:33.079 --> 00:09:36.350
I do not want pity.

00:09:36.360 --> 00:09:38.190
I'm not going to

00:09:38.190 --> 00:09:38.200
wallow

00:09:38.200 --> 00:09:41.990
in self-pity, period. I live by

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:46.829
faith. One night, I was at the sink

00:09:46.839 --> 00:09:48.269
doing dishes and I was just

00:09:48.279 --> 00:09:51.269
fussing to

00:09:51.269 --> 00:09:51.279
the

00:09:51.279 --> 00:09:53.430
Lord because

00:09:53.430 --> 00:09:53.440
I

00:09:53.440 --> 00:09:55.550
couldn't go

00:09:55.550 --> 00:09:55.560
to

00:09:57.550 --> 00:09:57.560
a

00:09:57.560 --> 00:09:59.990
church

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:02.829
cookout.

00:10:02.839 --> 00:10:05.190
I said, "God, do you not hear anything

00:10:05.200 --> 00:10:08.590
I pray? Where have you gone? Why am I

00:10:08.600 --> 00:10:12.110
still going through

00:10:12.110 --> 00:10:12.120
this?"All

00:10:12.120 --> 00:10:15.150
of a sudden,

00:10:18.880 --> 00:10:23.829
Jesus comes in the

00:10:23.839 --> 00:10:26.509
room. This was the

00:10:26.519 --> 00:10:29.150
first manifestation

00:10:29.150 --> 00:10:29.160
where

00:10:29.160 --> 00:10:33.069
I actually saw him; it wasn't a vision.

00:10:33.079 --> 00:10:36.110
He actually came into the kitchen. The

00:10:36.110 --> 00:10:36.120
manifested

00:10:36.120 --> 00:10:39.470
presence was so strong

00:10:42.480 --> 00:10:44.790
I turned around and hit the

00:10:44.800 --> 00:10:47.550
floor because I couldn't stand in his

00:10:47.560 --> 00:10:50.269
presence. I literally thought I was going

00:10:50.279 --> 00:10:52.790
to be melted like

00:10:52.800 --> 00:10:56.590
wax.

00:10:56.600 --> 00:10:58.910
My wife came around the corner because

00:10:58.910 --> 00:10:58.920
she could

00:10:58.920 --> 00:11:00.910
feel it too, and she said, "Oh

00:11:00.920 --> 00:11:03.190
my God, what is this? Are

00:11:03.200 --> 00:11:06.190
you dying? Is he

00:11:06.200 --> 00:11:08.150
taking

00:11:08.150 --> 00:11:08.160
you?"She

00:11:08.160 --> 00:11:09.949
couldn't see Jesus, but she could

00:11:09.959 --> 00:11:12.470
feel the presence of the Lord.

00:11:12.480 --> 00:11:15.790
I said, "No baby, Jesus is

00:11:15.800 --> 00:11:34.150
here."And

00:11:34.160 --> 00:11:35.629
he spoke to

00:11:35.639 --> 00:11:49.230
me. He said, "I've heard all your

00:11:49.240 --> 00:11:53.069
prayers.

00:11:59.760 --> 00:12:01.670
According to your faith, be it

00:12:01.680 --> 00:12:06.310
done unto

00:12:06.320 --> 00:12:09.470
you. What do you really have need of,

00:12:09.470 --> 00:12:09.480
Brandon?"I

00:12:09.480 --> 00:12:13.230
said, "Lord, don't you know?

00:12:13.240 --> 00:12:16.230
I need

00:12:16.240 --> 00:12:19.069
my little girl to be

00:12:19.069 --> 00:12:19.079
healed."He

00:12:19.079 --> 00:12:22.230
said, "According to your faith,

00:12:22.240 --> 00:12:25.670
son, be it done unto

00:12:25.680 --> 00:12:28.550
you. She will amend from this;

00:12:29.920 --> 00:12:37.670
it's going to be a

00:12:37.670 --> 00:12:37.680
process."He

00:12:37.680 --> 00:12:39.870
stood there for a little bit

00:12:39.880 --> 00:12:42.750
and loved on

00:12:42.760 --> 00:12:45.350
me,

00:12:45.360 --> 00:12:47.110
then

00:12:47.120 --> 00:12:55.870
he

00:12:55.880 --> 00:12:58.110
vanished. The presence of God was so

00:12:58.120 --> 00:13:00.590
strong on me.

00:13:00.600 --> 00:13:03.110
I didn't tell anybody other than my wife.

00:13:23.040 --> 00:13:25.629
This

00:13:25.639 --> 00:13:27.790
was on a Friday

00:13:27.800 --> 00:13:30.670
night.

00:13:33.639 --> 00:13:37.790
On Monday,

00:13:37.800 --> 00:13:41.710
her ABA therapist called. She said, "Hey

00:13:41.720 --> 00:13:45.030
Brandon, what did you do?

00:13:48.069 --> 00:13:48.079
Something

00:13:50.639 --> 00:13:52.790
happened over the

00:13:52.800 --> 00:13:55.710
weekend.

00:14:00.759 --> 00:14:05.350
You need to explain to me how

00:14:05.360 --> 00:14:07.509
she's talking in little sentences and

00:14:07.519 --> 00:14:09.550
saying

00:14:09.560 --> 00:14:13.110
words.

00:14:15.600 --> 00:14:21.870
It's like a light switch is coming

00:14:26.150 --> 00:14:26.160
on."I

00:14:30.959 --> 00:14:35.710
said, "Well, on

00:14:35.720 --> 00:14:46.910
Friday,

00:14:46.920 --> 00:14:49.110
Jesus

00:14:49.120 --> 00:14:53.150
came. He told me all things are possible

00:14:53.160 --> 00:14:54.430
to him that

00:14:58.839 --> 00:15:02.189
believes."Megan

00:15:06.600 --> 00:15:10.470
went from not saying anything

00:15:12.240 --> 00:15:15.829
for years to being able to say

00:15:15.839 --> 00:15:19.629
little things and sleeping through the

00:15:19.639 --> 00:15:23.189
night.

00:15:30.399 --> 00:15:36.590
She's 18 now and she's still

00:15:36.600 --> 00:15:38.949
overcoming. There was a

00:15:38.959 --> 00:15:42.910
time about five years ago that we had

00:15:42.920 --> 00:15:46.509
to give her eight Ex-Lax pills a day for

00:15:46.519 --> 00:15:49.350
her to have a bowel movement. We took her

00:15:49.360 --> 00:15:52.829
to Billy Burke in Tulsa.

00:15:59.279 --> 00:16:01.470
My son

00:16:01.480 --> 00:16:03.670
filmed it when he prayed for her.

00:16:43.519 --> 00:16:47.110
That night,

00:16:47.120 --> 00:16:50.309
she had a bowel movement on her own

00:16:50.319 --> 00:16:53.230
for the first time

00:16:53.240 --> 00:16:57.069
ever. She started having bowel movements

00:16:57.079 --> 00:16:59.150
every single day after we went to

00:16:59.160 --> 00:17:02.309
Tulsa and had that prayer

00:17:02.319 --> 00:17:06.510
service. A miracle is a

00:17:06.520 --> 00:17:09.789
miracle, even if it is a

00:17:09.799 --> 00:17:12.590
process. Our

00:17:12.590 --> 00:17:12.600
neuropsychologist

00:17:12.600 --> 00:17:15.429
told

00:17:15.439 --> 00:17:19.669
us, "You just need to move on and let her

00:17:19.679 --> 00:17:22.750
be a ward of the state.

